com.survivingwithandroid.weather.lib.provider

Interface IProviderType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ForecastIOProviderType, OpenweathermapProviderType, WeatherUndergroundProviderType, YahooProviderType

    public interface IProviderType
    This interface provides the description of the weather provider. For each weather provider implemented, there must be a class that implements this interface and provides the fully qualified class name of the provider and the fully qualified of the code provider
    Author:
    Francesco Azzola
